&lt;p&gt;As a key member of the marketing team, you’ll play a vital role in optimizing our acquisition funnel, running paid/unpaid campaigns, and driving performance across various channels. You’ll work closely with sales, product marketing, and demand gen to expand our reach, generate high-quality leads, and contribute to revenue growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a highly cross-functional, fully remote role that requires strong analytical skills, creativity, and a passion for continuous experimentation and improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
