&lt;li&gt;Content &amp;amp; Messaging: Help develop compelling messaging, ad copy, and landing pages to enhance campaign performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Test &amp;amp; Iterate: Run A/B tests across channels, optimizing creatives, audiences, and messaging to maximize ROI.&lt;/li&gt;
